<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Upanishads&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13" title="Edit section: Translations">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Translations</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.sacred-texts.com/hin/upan/index.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.sacred-texts.com/hin/upan/index.htm" rel="nofollow">Translations of major Upanishads</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.bharatadesam.com/spiritual/upanishads/aitareya_upanishad.php" class="external text" title="http://www.bharatadesam.com/spiritual/upanishads/aitareya_upanishad.php" rel="nofollow">11 principal Upanishads with translations</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.sankaracharya.org" class="external text" title="http://www.sankaracharya.org" rel="nofollow">Translations of principal Upanishads at sankaracharya.org</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.tititudorancea.com/z/vedanta.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.tititudorancea.com/z/vedanta.htm" rel="nofollow">Upanishads and other Vedanta texts</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.worldwidewonder.co.cc" class="external free" title="http://www.worldwidewonder.co.cc" rel="nofollow">http://www.worldwidewonder.co.cc</a></li>
